//! The Pekoscript standard library entry.
//!
//! Submodules resolve as sibling files: std::core is core.peko, std::io is
//! io.peko, and so on. std::core and std::collections are auto-imported and
//! used bare. std::runtime, std::xml, and std::json are auto-imported and used
//! through their prefix. Every other module needs an explicit import.
